Technical

Architecture

Frontend: React + wagmi hooks

Smart Contracts: LendingPool + Oracle Adapter on SL

Service: Node.js listener to track events and save loan status

Storage: PostgreSQL for logs, IPFS for metadata


Features

1. Deposit & earn yield


2. Borrow with over-collateralization


3. Automatic liquidation on collateral drop




